fm: int computeArea(int A, int B, int C, int D, int E, int F, int G, int H)      {         long x1 = max(A,E);         long y1 = max(B,F);         long x2 = min(C,G);         long y2 = min(D,H);                  long overlap;         if (x1>=x2 || y1>=y2)             overlap = 0;         else                  return (long)(C-A)*(D-B) + (long)(G-E)*(H-F) - overlap;     }
